description:
Domains parameter: Enter a CSV string of domains you would like to ignore from observable parsing results.  For value "domain.com", will ignore variants such as http://domain.com, https://another.sub.domain.com/folder/page.html, www.domain.com, etc.
IP CIDR Ranges parameter:  Enter a CSV string of IPv4/IPv6 CIDR ranges you would like to ignore from observable parsing results.  For value "10.0.0.0/8", will ignore variants such as 10.0.0.1, 10.255.255.255, http://10.10.1.2:443/page.html,  etc.
Regex: Enter a Pythonic regex of values you wish to ignore, i.e. (domain\.com)|(other-domain\.com)
name: Observable_Parser_Ignore_Lists
title: Observable Parser Ignore Lists
